Dano John Keahi <dano@notaryeveryday.com>
9:59 AM (2 minutes ago)
to mark.kyser

Good morning Mark,

As you know errors and fraud are rising in title transactions. Two out of ten real estate deals contain document mistakes, and fraudulent signings continue to grow, putting agencies at risk of delays, compliance issues, and financial loss.

At Notary Everyday we solve both problems. Our platform integrates with your systems and connects you with vetted, experienced notaries nationwide. We reduce errors and fight fraud through verification, geo verified signings, secure audit trails, and real time alerts.

Would you be open to a 30 minute call next week so we can demo the tech? Please share your team’s availability and I will send over a video link to connect.

Best regards, Dano

actions.description: I know my team reached out to you via email, and I wanted to personally connect here on LinkedIn as well. Our technology at Notary Everyday serves as the last line of defense against errors and fraud in the closing process. Looking forward to connecting with you!

actions.subject:

actions.description:
Good afternoon Kathy,

As you know errors and fraud are rising in title transactions. Two out of ten real estate deals contain document mistakes, and fraudulent signings continue to grow, putting agencies at risk of delays, compliance issues, and financial loss.

At Notary Everyday we solve both problems. Our platform integrates with your systems and connects you with vetted, experienced notaries nationwide. We reduce errors and fight fraud through verification, geo verified signings, secure audit trails, and real time alerts.

Would you be open to a 30 minute call next week? Please share your team’s availability and I will send over a video link to connect.

Best regards, Dano
